These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, basketball, biathlon, water-polo
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, lily, aconite, poppy
4 different games are played: snooker, canasta, domino, poker
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, gardening, puzzles, sudoku
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, turkish, argentine, indian
 1. the mexican is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 2. the person playing poker is between the person who's sport is surfing and the indian##2
 3. the person who's hobby is reading is the indian##1
 4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 5. the mexican is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person playing domino##2
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the argentine##1
 7. the turkish is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 8. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 9. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the indian##1
10. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |     4     |
| Sport           | biathlon | surfing   | water-polo | basketball |
| Flower   | begonia      | lily | aconite              | poppy |
| Game   | snooker       | canasta     | poker               | domino    |
| Hobby           | gardening        | puzzles     | sudoku           | reading       |
| Nationality     | turkish | argentine     | mexican                | indian      |

