 2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the game-smoker##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in march is between the alhambra-smoker and the japanese##2
 4. the person traveling to hannover is the person driving the skateboard##1
 5. the dutch is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 8. the person driving the van is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 9. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
10. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the french##1
11. the person driving the skateboard is the alhambra-smoker##1
12. the game-smoker is the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |     2      |       3        |      4      |
