 3. the person playing backgammon is between the bluemaster-smoker and the old-henry-smoker##2
 4. the craftsman house is the person who likes aquamarine##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who likes mauve##1
 6. the person playing backgammon is the dunhill-smoker##1
 7. the modern house is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 8. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
10. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in gothic-revivaling##1
11. the person who's birthday is in gothic-revivaling is between the person who likes mauve and the modern house##2
12. the person who's birthday is in july is between the craftsman house and the dunhill-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |    3     |     4      |
| Cigar      | old-henry      | dunhill         | bluemaster | siglo      |
| Color           | mauve | turquise | fuchsia | aquamarine     |
| Game   | poker         | backgammon          | scrabble  | snooker |
| Birthday         | may        | gothic-revivaling  | july | march   |
| House     | gothic-revival    | tower         | modern     | craftsman     |

