.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-18::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, rose, bellflower, dahlia
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, snooker, poker, canasta
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, siglo, swisher, havana
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, security-guard, photographer, journalist
House: cape-cod, tower, futuristic, colonial
 1. the havana-smoker is between the photographer and the tower house##2
 2. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 3. the security-guard is the futuristic house##1
 4. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far right##1
 5. the journalist is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
 6. the security-guard is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 7. the person who growsmarigold is the person playing canasta##1
 8. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 9. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person playing poker##1
10. the journalist is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
11. the person who growsdahlia is between the person playing canasta and the police-officer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |   4    |
| Flower          | marigold  | dahlia  | rose  | bellflower   |
| Game   | canasta     | mah-jongg | poker     | snooker |
| Cigar           | swisher   | havana     | siglo      | bluemaster   |
| Job         | photographer   | journalist    | police-officer  | security-guard |
| House     | cape-cod | colonial     | tower | futuristic |

