.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-19::.
House: gothic-revival, art-deco, farmhouse, wooden
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, scientific, time-travel, mystery
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, montecristo, old-henry, dunhill
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, sailing, handball, snowboarding
There 4 different types of food: banana, watermelon, cucumber, radish
 1. the old-henry-smoker is the person watching scientific movies##1
 2. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
 3. the art-deco house is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the dunhill-smoker##2
 4. the dunhill-smoker is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 5. the gothic-revival house is between the art-deco house and the person eating radish##2
 6. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 7. the person who's sport is handball is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching spy movies is the person eating cucumber##1
 9. the art-deco house is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
10. the farmhouse house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |       4       |
| House      | wooden    | art-deco     | gothic-revival        | farmhouse          |
| Movie-Genre         | mystery | scientific   | spy        | time-travel |
| Cigar           | oliveros   | old-henry | dunhill | montecristo      |
| Sport   | snowboarding    | sailing      | cricket          | handball        |
| Food     | banana  | watermelon   | cucumber      | radish           |

