.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-20::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, turtle, rabbit
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, july, october, january
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, epic, western, time-travel
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, havana, oliveros, prince
House: wooden, colonial, craftsman, townhouse
 1. the person who's birthday is in january is the person watching epic movies##1
 2. the townhouse house is between the person watching time-travel movies and the ritmeester-smoker##2
 3. the colonial house is between the havana-smoker and the craftsman house##2
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
 6. the havana-smoker is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is the oliveros-smoker##1
 9. the colonial house is on the left of the craftsman house##1
10. the owner of the ferret is the person watching disaster movies##1
11. the person watching disaster movies is the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Pet         | turtle  | guinea-pig | rabbit | ferret |
| Birthday   | january      | july   | october      | february    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | western | time-travel        | disaster     |
| Cigar         | ritmeester  | havana  | oliveros     | prince      |
| House     | wooden | townhouse      | colonial   | craftsman       |

 